Path: This week in Nu #80
Content:
fdncred fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3133] coercion errors for 
``$nothing``
 and 
``$variable``
, updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3120] ``fetch``
 to surf 2.2
, released a new version of 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/vscode-nushell-lang/releases/tag/v0.1.1] the Nushell VSCode extension
rezural added an 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3128] optional paging system
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3121] here
andrasio added back 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3126] preserving column order in json
kubouch added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3123] ``path join``
 and updated other path commands
, added option to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3114] invert match selections
LhKipp improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3112] host printing support
davidmalcolm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/106] fixed a typo in the book
stormasm clarified 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/107] how to think about let-env in the book
More scripts were added to the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts] nu scripts collection
